# asdf-ada: Configuration options

cat <<'EOF'
Environment variables for asdf-ada:

ASDF_ADA_SKIP_VERIFY
  Set to "true" to skip SHA256 checksum verification during download.
  Default: false

GITHUB_TOKEN / GITHUB_API_TOKEN
  GitHub personal access token to increase API rate limits.
  Useful if you encounter rate limiting during version listing.

Example usage:

  # Install without checksum verification
  ASDF_ADA_SKIP_VERIFY=true asdf install ada 14.1.0

  # Use GitHub token for API requests
  GITHUB_TOKEN=ghp_xxxx asdf install ada latest
EOF
